descriptionHtml:
ABOUT THE SKULLCANDY APP
Enhance and customize your listening experience with the Skullcandy App. Control product features and settings, access user guides and update new features as they become available through firmware over the air (FOTA) updates.

*This app is not compatible with all Skullcandy products.

The following Skullcandy audio products have app-enabled features:
- Crusher ANC
- Crusher Evo
- Grind Fuel
- Indy ANC
- Indy Evo
- Indy Fuel
- Push Active
- Push Ultra

If you do not have any of the above products, this app will not work for you.

PRODUCT FEATURE HIGHLIGHTS
Personal Sound: Hear your music like never before. Tune your Grind Fuel, Crusher ANC, Crusher Evo and Indy ANC to your unique hearing. Take a simple hearing test to generate your personalized sound profile.
Equalizers & Hearing Modes: Quick access to Stay-Aware and Ambient Modes let you easily manage changing noise environments and listening preferences.
Over the Air Firmware (FOTA) Updates: As they become available, we will release new and enhanced product features and deeper product customizations to the buds you own, delivering you the latest, greatest audio experience.

USER GUIDES & SUPPORT
Detailed user manuals and quick guides remind you how to get the most of your product.
